ths that no one else has taken...yet.', 3620, 0), (48266, 'Sometimes the only path we can maneuver is from the bed to the bathroom. That''s okay. Let your journey be what it is . Just keep moving.', 3620, 0), (48267, 'We navigate many paths each day, but how many sooth our souls and nourish our senses? Be aware of where you walk because the path you take can change your very essence.', 3620, 0), (48268, 'Nature makes the best paths that leads to the best places.', 3620, 0), (48269, 'The journey isn''t the vista at the end, it''s the ever changing view along the way.', 3620, 0), (48270, 'A wolf searches the path for prey that has paused. Keep moving.', 3620, 0), (48271, 'You do not have to know which path you must take. That''s not how life works. You simply must be curious and daring enough to take a step into the unknown. That''s how you come to know.', 3620, 0), (48272, 'The weight you life is not nearly as heavy as the weigh you carry.', 3620, 0), (48273, 'The weight you lift is not nearly as heavy as the weight you carry.', 3620, 0), (48274, 'Even during a mid-life crisis do not deviate from your goal. History remembers only those who succeed.', 6250, 0), (48275, 'Sometimes if you want to stand out,you at first have to blend in.', 2876, 0), (48276, 'No man can achieve success if he didn’t first know the value of time.', 3800, 0), (48277, 'Success in politics is the art of the timely lie.', 884, 0), (48278, 'The dream is over only when you have become complacent.', 11304, 0), (48279, 'Not all paths offer a vista. But every path offers a lesson.', 3620, 0), (48280, 'Pay attention to every person who crosses your path today. They are there for a reason.', 3620, 0), (48281, 'When you succeed in showing the real products that this disappearing life has produced, then you are said to be a winner.', 3800, 0), (48282, 'The highest level of success every moment is ‘being alive', 4632, 0), (48283, 'I did not find my way out of the darkness until I admitted I was lost.', 3