ic, you need to let your pretence of arrogance grow as big as a Dinosaur, so that the fake intellectuals start to realize their true inferiority in front of you.', 2874, 0), (49078, 'You must hiss at people who intend to undermine your individuality with their false pride and intellectual stupidity. You must frighten them away, lest they should do you harm. Act like you have a lot of venom inside you, but never inject them into anyone.', 2874, 0), (49079, 'Criticisms of a society filled with fools have no power in them to bother the sage that has emerged from the agonizing fire of misery.', 2874, 0), (49080, 'You can be good at many things, but you can only be great at one thing, until you find that thing, you are an average loser.', 4238, 0), (49081, 'Realize yourself. Realize your abilities. Be sincere to nobody else, but yourself. Keep walking on the path of bravery. Keep walking on the path of your passion. Keep walking, and do not stop until you reach your goal.', 2874, 0), (49082, 'Never focus your attention on what the world has to say about you. Rather turn your focus inside and listen to what your inner voice has to say to you. You can find the answers to the most complicated questions of life from your deepest self. Pay attention and listen. Your inner self has to say something to you. Listen to that eternal entity within, and you shall discover the way through which you’ll reach your goal.', 2874, 0), (49083, 'Never focus your attention on what the world has to say about you. Rather turn your focus inside and listen to what your inner voice has to say to you.', 2874, 0), (49084, 'Have faith in yourself. All the power is in your biology already. Be conscious of that power and bring it out. Remember, truth is indestructible, virtue is indestructible, purity is indestructible.', 2874, 0), (49085, 'Moral character is the DNA of success and happiness.', 6413, 0), (49086, 'All achievements begin with the simple cognitive faculties known as perception and imagination. Expand your perception. Expand your imagination. Be aware of your inner strength. Realize yourself. Realize your abilities. Be sincere to nobody else, but yourself. Keep walking on the path of bravery. Keep walking on the path of your passion. Keep walking, and do not stop until you reach your goal. And remember, there will always be another goal to be achieved. So, have pleasure from the pursuit.', 2874, 0), (49087, 'Pay attention and listen. Your inner self has to say something to you. Listen to that eternal entity within, and you shall discover the way through which you’ll reach your goal.', 2874, 0), (49088, '​You can find the answers to the most complicated questions of life from your deepest self. Pay attention and listen.', 2874, 0), (49089, 'Pain is our salvation ''cos when it''s dark enough, a star will reveal itself.', 11381, 0), (49090, 'Someone is always feeding fat off everything you don''t know.', 11381, 0), (49091, 'The idea that sins can be forgiven is at the root of mankind''s problems. Everyone pays...sooner or later.', 11381, 0), (49092, 'Be excellent in your own terms. Do not look for approval from a single soul on this planet. Respect yourself and in time the whole world will respect you. It is a tragedy of modern life that the light of truth scares the society much more than the darkness of ignorance.', 2874, 0), (49093, 'Respect yourself and in time the whole world will respect you.', 2874, 0), (49094, 'The more you worry about your spending, the less you focus on increasing your capacity.', 11381, 0), (49095, 'Light up the radiant flame of conscience, goodwill and compassion in your heart, and go over the length and breadth of your society in the pursuit of shedding light over the whole world. And in time, you’ll become a glorious sun that will shine over the entire human population.', 2874, 0), (49096, '​Let the lotus of your character be full-blown and the results will follow.', 2874, 0), (49097, 'Be brave and upright. Shred the fake